														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1955326">
									

<p>Just starting to dig into this cannon, and I'm really enjoying it so far. I'm surprised this doesn't have more up-votes, but I suppose the length might be scaring some people off. It is well worth it, though.</p>
<p>I really like the world-building done here, and the way every piece of the cannon fits together logically. I noticed some similarities to Dresden Files, at least in the way magic works and the hints at the Faerie Courts. Was that an inspiration for this?</p>
<p>Anyway, this is quite good. I can't wait to read the next entries.</p>

							</div>

								
					
