<p>This tale was great from start to finish. I'm just starting to get into the GOC, and this tale really makes me wanna get into them and their lore and I'll definitely be reading more of this canon. I loved the world building and it was really cool getting to see The Foundation from the perspective of the GOC.</p>
<p>Also it was nice to see Lombardi :D</p>

